(1) Uninstalling Packages From Project (Syntax)
-----------------------------------------------
==> npm uninstall Package_Name

EX:
-----
==> npm uninstall moment // This Will Uninstall 'moment' But Not Remove It From Package.json Dependency
==> npm uninstall moment --save // This Will Uninstall 'moment' And Remove It From Package.json Dependency
==> npm uninstall moment --save-dev // This Will Uninstall 'moment' And Remove It From Package.json Dev-Dependency

